## üöÄ Setup Instructions

### Prerequisites
- n8n instance (cloud or self-hosted)
- Google Sheets API credentials
- Gmail/Telegram credentials
- API2PDF API key (for PDF generation)

### Installation
1. Import JSON workflow file to n8n
2. Configure credentials for each service
3. Update Google Sheet IDs
4. Test manually before scheduling
5. Activate workflow

### Configuration
- Modify schedule triggers as needed
- Update recipient lists in Google Sheets
- Customize chart colors/styles in HTTP nodes
- Adjust analysis thresholds in JavaScript nodes

